{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1007,"text":"In my previous life, I was an artist."},{"time":4494,"text":"I still paint. I love art."},{"time":6967,"text":"I love the joy that color can give to our lives"},{"time":12566,"text":"and to our communities,"},{"time":15214,"text":"and I try to bring something of the artist in me"},{"time":20493,"text":"in my politics,"},{"time":22614,"text":"and I see"},{"time":26542,"text":"part of my job today, the reason for being here,"},{"time":31726,"text":"not just to campaign for my party,"},{"time":36653,"text":"but for politics, and the role it can play"},{"time":41358,"text":"for the better in our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45174,"text":"For 11 years, I was mayor of Tirana, our capital."},{"time":51046,"text":"We faced many challenges."},{"time":53738,"text":"Art was part of the answer,"},{"time":56222,"text":"and my name, in the very beginning,"},{"time":58840,"text":"was linked with two things:"},{"time":61255,"text":"demolition of illegal constructions"},{"time":65348,"text":"in order to get public space back,"},{"time":69428,"text":"and use of colors in order to revive the hope"},{"time":73106,"text":"that had been lost in my city."},{"time":76425,"text":"But this use of colors was not just an artistic act."},{"time":82286,"text":"Rather, it was a form of political action"},{"time":86402,"text":"in a context when the city budget I had available"},{"time":91504,"text":"after being elected amounted to zero comma something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98211,"text":"When we painted the first building,"},{"time":101202,"text":"by splashing a radiant orange on the somber gray"},{"time":105754,"text":"of a facade,"},{"time":108018,"text":"something unimaginable happened."},{"time":112242,"text":"There was a traffic jam"},{"time":114312,"text":"and a crowd of people gathered"},{"time":117317,"text":"as if it were the location of some spectacular accident,"},{"time":122235,"text":"or the sudden sighting of a visiting pop star."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126954,"text":"The French E.U. official in charge of the funding"},{"time":131756,"text":"rushed to block the painting."},{"time":134850,"text":"He screeched that he would block the financing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139596,"text":"\"But why?\" I asked him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143226,"text":"\"Because the colors you have ordered"},{"time":146018,"text":"do not meet European standards,\" he replied."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150730,"text":"\"Well,\" I told him,"},{"time":153659,"text":"\"the surroundings do not meet European standards,"},{"time":156847,"text":"even though this is not what we want,"},{"time":162142,"text":"but we will choose the colors ourselves,"},{"time":165313,"text":"because this is exactly what we want."},{"time":168983,"text":"And if you do not let us continue with our work,"},{"time":172866,"text":"I will hold a press conference here,"},{"time":175540,"text":"right now, right in this road,"},{"time":178816,"text":"and we will tell people that you look to me"},{"time":182066,"text":"just like the censors of the socialist realism era.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":187940,"text":"Then he was kind of troubled,"},{"time":190595,"text":"and asked me for a compromise."},{"time":193187,"text":"But I told him no, I'm sorry,"},{"time":195507,"text":"compromise in colors is gray,"},{"time":200009,"text":"and we have enough gray to last us a lifetime."},{"time":205097,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":206314,"text":"So it's time for change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211433,"text":"The rehabilitation of public spaces"},{"time":213603,"text":"revived the feeling of belonging"},{"time":216337,"text":"to a city that people lost."},{"time":221206,"text":"The pride of people about their own place of living,"},{"time":227646,"text":"and there were feelings that had been buried"},{"time":231065,"text":"deep for years under the fury of the illegal,"},{"time":235720,"text":"barbaric constructions that sprang up in the public space."},{"time":241194,"text":"And when colors came out everywhere,"},{"time":244238,"text":"a mood of change started transforming the spirit of people."},{"time":248726,"text":"Big noise raised up: \"What is this? What is happening?"},{"time":251673,"text":"What are colors doing to us?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":253634,"text":"And we made a poll,"},{"time":254689,"text":"the most fascinating poll I've seen in my life."},{"time":257091,"text":"We asked people, \"Do you want this action,"},{"time":264348,"text":"and to have buildings painted like that?\""},{"time":268838,"text":"And then the second question was,"},{"time":271209,"text":"\"Do you want it to stop or do you want it to continue?\""},{"time":274213,"text":"To the first question,"},{"time":275897,"text":"63 percent of people said yes, we like it."},{"time":279803,"text":"Thirty-seven said no, we don't like it."},{"time":282163,"text":"But to the second question, half of them that didn't like it,"},{"time":285835,"text":"they wanted it to continue. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":288914,"text":"So we noticed change."},{"time":292041,"text":"People started to drop less litter in the streets, for example,"},{"time":296436,"text":"started to pay taxes,"},{"time":299066,"text":"started to feel something they had forgotten,"},{"time":303515,"text":"and beauty was acting as a guardsman"},{"time":308579,"text":"where municipal police, or the state itself, were missing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315121,"text":"One day I remember walking along a street"},{"time":318822,"text":"that had just been colored,"},{"time":321418,"text":"and where we were in the process of planting trees,"},{"time":325197,"text":"when I saw a shopkeeper and his wife"},{"time":328442,"text":"putting a glass facade to their shop."},{"time":332409,"text":"They had thrown the old shutter"},{"time":334706,"text":"in the garbage collection place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337698,"text":"\"Why did you throw away the shutters?\" I asked him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341258,"text":"\"Well, because the street is safer now,\" they answered."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346490,"text":"\"Safer? Why? They have posted more policemen here?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":352058,"text":"\"Come on, man! What policemen?"},{"time":354882,"text":"You can see it for yourself. There are colors,"},{"time":357974,"text":"streetlights, new pavement with no potholes,"},{"time":363794,"text":"trees. So it's beautiful; it's safe.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":368586,"text":"And indeed, it was beauty that was giving people"},{"time":372530,"text":"this feeling of being protected."},{"time":376957,"text":"And this was not a misplaced feeling."},{"time":380459,"text":"Crime did fall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385216,"text":"The freedom that was won in 1990"},{"time":388562,"text":"brought about a state of anarchy in the city,"},{"time":392699,"text":"while the barbarism of the '90s"},{"time":395610,"text":"brought about a loss of hope for the city."},{"time":399092,"text":"The paint on the walls did not feed children,"},{"time":403362,"text":"nor did it tend the sick or educate the ignorant,"},{"time":407426,"text":"but it gave hope and light,"},{"time":410867,"text":"and helped to make people see"},{"time":413307,"text":"there could be a different way of doing things,"},{"time":416410,"text":"a different spirit, a different feel to our lives,"},{"time":420321,"text":"and that if we brought the same energy and hope"},{"time":426540,"text":"to our politics, we could build a better life"},{"time":430828,"text":"for each other and for our country."},{"time":436023,"text":"We removed 123,000 tons of concrete"},{"time":442873,"text":"only from the riverbanks."},{"time":445480,"text":"We demolished more than 5,000 illegal buildings"},{"time":450630,"text":"all over the city,"},{"time":453612,"text":"up to eight stories high, the tallest of them."},{"time":458081,"text":"We planted 55,000 trees and bushes in the streets."},{"time":464610,"text":"We established a green tax,"},{"time":467693,"text":"and then everybody accepted it"},{"time":471723,"text":"and all businessmen paid it regularly."},{"time":476717,"text":"By means of open competitions,"},{"time":479104,"text":"we managed to recruit in our administration"},{"time":482097,"text":"many young people,"},{"time":484092,"text":"and we thus managed to build"},{"time":485954,"text":"a de-politicized public institution"},{"time":489225,"text":"where men and women were equally represented."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493745,"text":"International organizations"},{"time":496287,"text":"have invested a lot in Albania during these 20 years,"},{"time":499665,"text":"not all of it well spent."},{"time":502897,"text":"When I told the World Bank directors"},{"time":506025,"text":"that I wanted them to finance a project to build"},{"time":510938,"text":"a model reception hall for citizens"},{"time":513833,"text":"precisely in order to fight endemic daily corruption,"},{"time":517993,"text":"they did not understand me."},{"time":520243,"text":"But people were waiting in long queues"},{"time":523521,"text":"under sun and under rain"},{"time":526444,"text":"in order to get a certificate or just a simple answer"},{"time":530669,"text":"from two tiny windows of two metal kiosks."},{"time":538107,"text":"They were paying in order to skip the queue,"},{"time":542291,"text":"the long queue."},{"time":544647,"text":"The reply to their requests was met"},{"time":548610,"text":"by a voice coming from this dark hole,"},{"time":553311,"text":"and, on the other hand,"},{"time":557553,"text":"a mysterious hand coming out to take their documents"},{"time":562995,"text":"while searching through old documents for the bribe."},{"time":568803,"text":"We could change the invisible clerks within the kiosks,"},{"time":573110,"text":"every week, but we could not change this corrupt practice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578749,"text":"\"I'm convinced,\" I told a German official"},{"time":582523,"text":"with the World Bank,"},{"time":585299,"text":"\"that it would be impossible for them to be bribed"},{"time":589141,"text":"if they worked in Germany,"},{"time":591595,"text":"in a German administration,"},{"time":593546,"text":"just as I am convinced that if you put German officials"},{"time":597952,"text":"from the German administration in those holes,"},{"time":601175,"text":"they would be bribed just the same.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":605323,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":612027,"text":"It's not about genes."},{"time":613859,"text":"It's not about some being with a high conscience"},{"time":619593,"text":"and some others having not a conscience."},{"time":622035,"text":"It's about system, it's about organization."},{"time":624807,"text":"It's also about environment and respect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":628067,"text":"We removed the kiosks."},{"time":630950,"text":"We built the bright new reception hall"},{"time":634646,"text":"that made people, Tirana citizens,"},{"time":638217,"text":"think they had traveled abroad when they entered"},{"time":641903,"text":"to make their requests."},{"time":644327,"text":"We created an online system of control"},{"time":647771,"text":"and so speeded up all the processes."},{"time":651687,"text":"We put the citizen first, and not the clerks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656343,"text":"The corruption in the state administration"},{"time":660547,"text":"of countries like Albania --"},{"time":663247,"text":"it's not up to me to say also like Greece --"},{"time":667423,"text":"can be fought only by modernization."},{"time":672803,"text":"Reinventing the government by reinventing politics itself"},{"time":677555,"text":"is the answer, and not reinventing people"},{"time":681074,"text":"based on a ready-made formula"},{"time":683722,"text":"that the developed world often tries in vain to impose"},{"time":687978,"text":"to people like us."},{"time":690084,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":692791,"text":"Things have come to this point"},{"time":694775,"text":"because politicians in general,"},{"time":697267,"text":"but especially in our countries, let's face it,"},{"time":700163,"text":"think people are stupid."},{"time":702626,"text":"They take it for granted that, come what may,"},{"time":706170,"text":"people have to follow them,"},{"time":708382,"text":"while politics, more and more, fails to offer answers"},{"time":712476,"text":"for their public concerns"},{"time":716499,"text":"or the exigencies of the common people."},{"time":721170,"text":"Politics has come to resemble"},{"time":723972,"text":"a cynical team game played by politicians,"},{"time":727458,"text":"while the public has been pushed aside"},{"time":731387,"text":"as if sitting on the seats of a stadium"},{"time":735274,"text":"in which passion for politics"},{"time":737124,"text":"is gradually making room for blindness and desperation."},{"time":742733,"text":"Seen from those stairs, all politicians today"},{"time":747627,"text":"seem the same,"},{"time":749590,"text":"and politics has come to resemble"},{"time":754227,"text":"a sport that inspires more aggressiveness"},{"time":758828,"text":"and pessimism than social cohesion"},{"time":762140,"text":"and the desire for civic protaganism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":766413,"text":"Barack Obama won"},{"time":768439,"text":"— (Applause) —"},{"time":774716,"text":"because he mobilized people as never before"},{"time":778279,"text":"through the use of social networks."},{"time":780812,"text":"He did not know each and every one of them,"},{"time":783925,"text":"but with an admirable ingenuity,"},{"time":787795,"text":"he managed to transform them into activists"},{"time":791175,"text":"by giving them all the possibility to hold in their hands"},{"time":795304,"text":"the arguments and the instruments that each would need"},{"time":798898,"text":"to campaign in his name by making his own campaign."},{"time":803691,"text":"I tweet. I love it."},{"time":805746,"text":"I love it because it lets me get the message out,"},{"time":811115,"text":"but it also lets people get their messages to me."},{"time":815382,"text":"This is politics, not from top down,"},{"time":818374,"text":"but from the bottom up, and sideways,"},{"time":821598,"text":"and allowing everybody's voice to be heard"},{"time":824590,"text":"is exactly what we need."},{"time":826550,"text":"Politics is not just about leaders."},{"time":828604,"text":"It's not just about politicians and laws."},{"time":831365,"text":"It is about how people think,"},{"time":833333,"text":"how they view the world around them,"},{"time":835668,"text":"how they use their time and their energy."},{"time":838194,"text":"When people say all politicians are the same,"},{"time":840710,"text":"ask yourself if Obama was the same as Bush,"},{"time":843990,"text":"if François Hollande is the same as Sarkozy."},{"time":847565,"text":"They are not. They are human beings with different views"},{"time":852269,"text":"and different visions for the world."},{"time":854851,"text":"When people say nothing can change,"},{"time":857749,"text":"just stop and think what the world was like"},{"time":861813,"text":"10, 20, 50, 100 years ago."},{"time":866445,"text":"Our world is defined by the pace of change."},{"time":869561,"text":"We can all change the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":872365,"text":"I gave you a very small example"},{"time":875241,"text":"of how one thing, the use of color,"},{"time":878742,"text":"can make change happen."},{"time":881253,"text":"I want to make more change"},{"time":882616,"text":"as Prime Minister of my country,"},{"time":885404,"text":"but every single one of you can make change happen"},{"time":889726,"text":"if you want to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":891319,"text":"President Roosevelt, he said,"},{"time":894444,"text":"\"Believe you can, and you are halfway there.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":898117,"text":"Efharisto and kalinihta."}]},{"cues":[{"time":901184,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}